    "description": "methodical is a Bioconductor package that identifies genomic regions where DNA methylation is correlated with transcription, revealing transcript-proximal methylation-associated regulatory sites (TMRs). It combines RNA-seq and whole genome bisulfite sequencing (WGBS) data to refine regulatory logic in normal and tumor tissues.",
